### 8. `packages/pixelart/src/pixelart-provider.ts`
Provider factory. Key design:
- `PixelArtProviderSettings` interface: `apiKey?`, `baseURL?` (default `https://api.pixelart.ai/v1`), `headers?`, `fetch?`
- `PixelArtProvider` interface extending `ProviderV3`: exposes `image(modelId)` and `imageModel(modelId)` methods; `languageModel` and `embeddingModel` throw `NoSuchModelError`
